  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Select a color in the 'Calendar foreground color' ComboBox and open calendar of the demonstrated <em>DateTimePicker </em>and its foreground color will be corresponding with the selected color.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>DateTimePicker </em>contains the <em>CalendarForeColor </em>property that determinates the foreground color to the calendar.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>